Package com.photos.controllers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminController
    AdminController class: loads the admin screen and displays all existing users
    AlbumCardController
    AlbumCardController class: used to create objects that are displayed on the home page
    AlbumDetailsController
    AlbumDetailsController gets the details about a selected Album object
    ComboBoxModalController
    ComboBoxModalController class used for combobox scene
    ConfirmationModalController
    ConfirmationModalController class used to create confirmation modals
    DoubleInputModalController
    DoubleInputModalController class: sets up screens with double input
    EditPictureController
    EditPictureController class: allows changes to be made to an individual picture object
    HeaderController
    HeaderController class used for setting up the header
    HomeController
    HomeController class: loads in all albums for the current user
    LoginController
    LoginController class handles login
    PictureCardController
    PictureCardController class used to create PhotoCard objects for the album details
    SearchController
    SearchController used for the search function
    SidebarController
    SidebarController class: used for controller classes that have a sidebar menu
    SingleInputModalController
    SingleInputModalController class is used to create modals that require a single line of input.
    SlideshowController
    SlideshowController class used for displaying the slideshow
    TagController
    TagController class used to handle Tags
    UserCardController
    UserCardController class used to populate admin page
